name: Something's On The Station!?
description:
Please use fullscreen!

Welcome to being Captain of the state of the art space station, The Deimos 1! You will be taking part in multiple training simulations so you can be the very best captain you can be! For today's video you will be learning something incredibly crucial to your time on the spaceship!! Today you will learn WHAT TO DO IF AN ALIEN INVADES YOUR STATION!!!

And remember: Reach for the Stars!!!

CONTENT WARNING: Blood, Gore, Adult Language, Depictions of Violence, Disturbing Content. 16+ age range.

Writing, Visual Assets, Sound Design, Creative Direction and Intro Video by Camryn Graffius.

Programming, UI, some Visual Assets and Sound Design by Maxwell Gonzalez.

Voice Talent by K Newton.
